    TraversableGraph<MergedTargetNode>

    public class MergedTargetGraph
extends DirectedAcyclicGraph<MergedTargetNode>
    Target graph version where node is a set of all nodes with the same UnflavoredBuildTarget.

    This utility exists to support legacy configured buck query, and should not be used for anything else.
